To run: 

1. get a list of levels from the frodo sql explorer: 

http://fellowship.hackbrightacademy.com/explorer/34/?params=cohort_id%3A<<cohort id>> 
(replace <<cohort id>> with the actual cohort id; e.g. f17g)

2. Export the csv file from the sql explorer

3. Save it to this directory and call it levels.csv, removing the "name,level" 
first line

4. Run the script (it's randomized) until you get a result you like. The 
results will be saved in YYYYMMDD_pastpairs.csv so that it can be used next
go-around to avoid repeating partners. 

5. Profit. 


Query, for reference: 

SELECT CONCAT(first_name, ' ', last_name) AS name, sis_studentlevel.level
FROM sis_student
JOIN sis_studentlevel ON sis_student.id = sis_studentlevel.student_id
JOIN sis_cohorthouse ON sis_student.house_id = sis_cohorthouse.id
WHERE sis_student.cohort_id='$$cohort_id$$'
  AND sis_studentlevel.created IN
    (SELECT MAX(sis_studentlevel.created)
     FROM sis_studentlevel
     JOIN sis_student ON sis_student.id = sis_studentlevel.student_id
     GROUP BY sis_student.id)
GROUP BY sis_cohorthouse.title,
         sis_student.id,
         sis_studentlevel.level,
         sis_studentlevel.created
ORDER BY sis_cohorthouse.title, sis_student.last_name;
